-- Carlo Tassara finds buyers for Alior stake at PLN 79/shr -sources
-- By Adrian Krajewski
-- Wed Apr 23, 2014 04:34AM EDT
-- None



WARSAW, April 23 (Reuters) - The Carlo Tassara Group has found buyers for a 4.7-percent stake in Poland's mid-tier lender Alior Bank <ALRR.WA> at 79 zlotys per share, two market sources told Reuters on Wednesday.

The price values the stake at almost 261 million zlotys ($86 million) and comes in below the current market price of 80.43 zlotys per share - already 5.23 percent down on the day.